{
  "stem": "150.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I realized that this whole thing was abnormal, but pretty soon I fell into the, more or less, routine of the whole situation.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were many children at first because they weren't-- they really didn't start picking on children and start exterminating seriously at first.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not at that point.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later on, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What happened was that-- well, to begin with, what, what happened almost immediately was that the Germans announced that they needed 2,000 young men, and they needed them with college educations, preferably fluent in two out of three languages-- Russian, Lithuanian, and German.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that these people would be given a chance to do easy work, research at universities, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it sounded absolutely marvelous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So anybody who had any protection, any pull, tried to get in in those 2,000.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then the day came, and they marched out, the best and the brightest we had.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they took them to a place called the Ninth Fort, which was about 10 miles out of the city, an old World War I Russian fortress.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this is where they were killing people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were bringing in people there from Lithuania, but also from Germany and from France and from all over the place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it wasn't anything sophisticated, just machine guns and bulldozers and so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they killed the 2,000.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were never seen again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then the other-- the next thing that happened was that they announced that all of the gold, and silver, and valuables, and furs, and radios, watches, clocks, all that, had to be delivered within 72 hours.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they apparently felt that they weren't getting enough, so they decided to show us that they were serious about it.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
